se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider

  • Packages that use se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider 
    Package Description
    se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider
    This library introduces the concept of a "metadata provider" which is a wrapper around a MetadataResolver and allows for easier access to SAML metadata.
  • Classes in se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider used by se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider 
    Class Description
    AbstractMetadataProvider
    Abstract base class for the MetadataProvider interface.
    MetadataProvider
    An interface that offers methods that operate on one or several metadata sources.
